oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Prize Hereford
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white picture of Mr. B. Oles, Oak Ridge Farms, of Kingsville, Md., and one of his prize Herefords at the Southeastern Hereford Show in Clarksville, Tenn. Two other men are grooming the cow. A few other cows can be seen laying down.
